<paragraph blockId="32.[189,1398,1928,2027]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">The cellular details of the specimen examined were not clearly visible; thus, we were unable to obtain cell size information. The inner endocarp surface was also decayed but we were able to distinguish a few papillae.</paragraph>
